language ESSENCE' 2.0

letting elems be 3
letting setsize be 2
letting nbsets be elems ^ setsize

find m : matrix indexed by [int(1..nbsets), int(1..setsize)] of int(1..elems)

such that
    $ forall i : int(1..nbsets-1) . m[i,..] <lex m[i+1,..],
    forall i, j : int(1..nbsets) . ((i != j) => !(forall k : int(1..setsize) . m[i,k] = m[j,k])),
    $ forall i : int(1..nbsets) . alldifferent(m[i,..]),
    true
